item.title: CVE-2020-5349|2024-08-04T08:30:23.429Z -- dell -- networking
item.description: Dell EMC Networking S4100 and S5200 Series Switches manufactured prior to February 2020 contain a hardcoded credential vulnerability. A remote unauthenticated malicious user could exploit this vulnerability and gain administrative privileges.
